ZH: 我估计明天会下雨。
EN: I estimate that it will rain tomorrow.

ZH: 他估计要过几天才能恢复。
EN: He estimates that it will take a few days for him to recover.

ZH: 估计这个报告需要一个小时完成。
EN: It is estimated that this report will take an hour to complete.

ZH: 他估计这个项目需要两周时间。
EN: He estimates that this project will take two weeks.

ZH: 估计这个地方有三千年的历史。
EN: It is estimated that this place has a history of three thousand years.

ZH: 他估计她的年龄在三十左右。
EN: He estimates her age to be around thirty.

ZH: 估计这项工程总费用将超过一百万美元。
EN: It is estimated that the total cost of this project will exceed one million dollars.

ZH: 我估计那个人是个老板。
EN: I estimate that person to be a boss.

ZH: 估计我们需要更多的材料来完成这个任务。
EN: It is estimated that we need more materials to complete this task.

